reviewText: It proved to be quite entertaining and enjoyable.  I'd recommend it to anyone!  Any GGW video really delivers.
It was again Ok for those who are into soft core but the title is somewhat a misrepresentation of what is featured. Great for first time watchers of GGW!
I HATED it.  I have about 15 other GGW videos that I love, but this one completely disapointed me.  The "solo" scenes aren't at all what you would expect from this franchise.  Three thumbs down!
In a nutshell, this one sucked.  Not even sexy like past ones of girl/girl or solo action.  Basically they just showed facial closeups of the girls doing their thing or them moaning.  Boring!

I bought this and three other titles for a Batchelor Party as "Live" entertainment was verbotten, and besides, it was held at the beach and there wasn't any available. Anyway, it was typical GGW fare and really nothing to write home about. If you've seen one you've seen them all in my opinion. I watched some of this before I decided to do some fishing. I know that one girl in there was also in the 18th Birthday thing and it was obviously a different time and place. I guess they have "regulars" that turn up year after year. Fortunately, I wasn't saddled with them afterwards as they were bought from me. I just hope that these people gain some maturity along the way, because it scares me to realize that someday, some of these people may be in Government. That was my thoughts in the late 60's when I was in service and watching all the hippie protestors at the time. Unfortunately, I think that may well have been the case and some are now in Congress. Anyway, this is nothing but mindless stuff and maybe suitable for a Batchelor Party, but little else. Charlie S.

If you like a lot of flashing and boob tease this one probably is not for you. First G/G sequence on  the bed and on the floor. Lots of skin. Just so so. Next comes a solo. Camera picks up a girl on the beach and follows her to her room. Then she goes into one hell of a solo performance. A real doll to. She can eat crackers in my bed any day. After that and a few flash and tease scenes we get the final G/G sequence. It's a good one and takes us to the end of the show.
